m_q.target_metric: Box office revenue from national films in 2013
sub_questions: What is the total box office revenue for each country in 2013?
What percentage of each country's box office comes from national films in 2013?
Which country has the highest absolute revenue from national films in 2013?

schema_conflicts: Multiple rows with same Rank value (e.g., Rank 1 appears twice)
Inconsistent Year values within same dataset
World entry appears in middle of country list

scale_issues: Box Office values contain '$' and 'billion' text
Box office from national films contains percentage values with year references in parentheses
Need to convert text values to numeric for calculation

format_notes: Box Office column contains currency symbols and text
Box office from national films column contains mixed formats (percentages with year references, dashes)
Some rows have missing Rank values
Data appears to contain multiple years mixed together

constraints: Box office from national films must be a valid percentage for 2013
Box Office must be convertible to numeric value
derived_filters: Filter rows where Box office from national films contains '(2013)'
Remove rows with '–' in Box office from national films
statistical_tests: Check for duplicate countries in 2013 data
Verify year consistency in percentage references
output_format_requirements: Calculated national films revenue in USD
